name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 50: What’s a door?

content.html:
Dear Internet, This week is a good one. We had a lot of fun talking about what a door is? I mean, really when you think about it. What are they? We chat about bringing pets to work, adding a portcullis to your room, and Christmas presents. Stay gold, XOXO We are a new show, and would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick Bristow, Jennifer Cheek, Michael DiMauro, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
